<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shift Email</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            color: #222222;
        }
        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #185caf;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>MediSHIFT-ALIGN</h1>
            <h1>Shift Assignment Details</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello Staff, you have a shift assigned to you. Below are the details:</p>
            <p><strong>location:</strong> <%= location %></p>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= time %></p>
            <p><strong>Type:</strong> <%= type %></p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= duration %></p>
            <p><strong>Patient:</strong> <%= patient %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="uzairthreestar1456@gmail.com">uzairthreestar1456@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
